				\begin{document}$$R_0$$\end{document}R0, thereby effectively controlling the spread of the epidemic. The function enhances the model’s adaptability to various transmission mechanisms, better fits real epidemic data, and provides strong support for public health decision-making, helping to formulate more precise control strategies.

